        <div class="mt-0.5 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">The Matrix Primitive</div>
        <div class="mt-0.5 text-xs text-slate-600">Two scenarios, one form, a live delta bar picks a winner.</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/scenarios/" class="block rounded-md border border-cyan-200 bg-white p-3 transition hover:border-cyan-500 hover:bg-cyan-50">
        <div class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-600">Scenarios</div>
        <div class="mt-0.5 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">The Triad Primitive</div>
